00:01:05,110 --> 00:01:07,110
So Yun Yin died in a fire?

2
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,840
If she had died in the blaze,

3
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,120
that would have been a relief.

4
00:01:17,430 --> 00:01:18,840
But she didn't die right away.

5
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:21,350
Her whole body was burned.

6
00:01:22,230 --> 00:01:23,400
She also developed a lung disease.

7
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,430
She couldn't even think about performing anymore,

8
00:01:25,790 --> 00:01:27,230
even eating became difficult.

9
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:30,640
She suffered for months before she finally died.

10
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,760
So how do you know all this?

11
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:37,840
My sister found me back then.

12
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:40,280
We exchanged letters for a year.

13
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,350
About her situation,

14
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:45,280
I learned some of it from her letters.

15
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,480
The rest

16
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:51,150
came from my sister's old maid,

17
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,870
who told me before she passed away.

18
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:55,120
So you became a maid in the Xu family

19
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,280
to get revenge?

20
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:06,430
She was my sister to begin with.

21
00:02:08,350 --> 00:02:09,200
For her sake,

22
00:02:09,430 --> 00:02:11,200
giving up some freedom is nothing.

23
00:02:11,430 --> 00:02:12,120
But why

24
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:14,430
did you hurt those innocent brides?

25
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,430
I was helping them.

26
00:02:24,710 --> 00:02:26,000
I was helping them.

27
00:02:28,190 --> 00:02:31,870
Back then, Xu Qiyan asked a Taoist for a resurrection ritual.

28
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:35,870
He needed five women to bring my sister back to life.

29
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,680
The first bride he married after that was named Wu.

30
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,870
To help Wu escape,

31
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:45,030
I pretended to be a ghost to distract the Xu family.

32
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,800
But Xu Qiyan was actually pleased.

33
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,400
He thought my sister's spirit had appeared.

34
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:55,710
If my sister's spirit really is watching from above,

35
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:59,470
the first person she'd want to kill would be Xu Qiyan.

36
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:02,000
But how did Wu die?

37
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:10,080
When she tried to escape

38
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:13,520
in a panic

39
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:17,000
she fell into the lake and drowned

40
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:20,750
It was my fault she died

41
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:23,910
No

42
00:03:24,430 --> 00:03:25,030
No

43
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:27,030
I was helping her

44
00:03:27,470 --> 00:03:28,630
I was saving her

45
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:30,360
I was saving all of them

46
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:35,310
If she lived, she would only suffer

47
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:37,750
Just like my sister

48
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:41,430
But I didn't have the power to let them go

49
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:43,960
I was helping them too

50
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:46,710
It was that Taoist

51
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:49,150
It was that Taoist

52
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:53,000
He said my sister could be brought back to life

53
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,150
Did you ever ask what they wanted?

54
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:56,870
Someone like you

55
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:59,710
How are you any different from Xu Qiyan?

56
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:16,910
Qiao'er

57
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:21,710
I will go to the underworld to atone to them

58
00:04:23,590 --> 00:04:25,800
I won't let Xu Qiyan get near them again

59
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,600
Young master

60
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:30,800
Do you know

61
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,600
those years

62
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:37,720
were the happiest days of Qiao'er's life

63
00:04:39,310 --> 00:04:41,240
Osmanthus cake is so delicious

64
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:46,040
Qiao'er wants to have another piece

65
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,190
Alright

66
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,830
Qiao'er, be good

67
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,310
I'll take you to eat osmanthus cake

68
